    <string name="q1_title">How to scan a QR code?</string>
    <string name="q1_answer">Tap the \'Scan QR / Barcode\' button on the home screen and point your camera at the code. It will be detected automatically.</string>
    <string name="q2_title">Where can I find my scan history?</string>
    <string name="q2_answer">All your scans are saved automatically. You can access them by tapping the \'History\' card on the home screen.</string>
    <string name="q3_title">How to generate a QR code?</string>
    <string name="q3_answer">Go to \'Generate QR\', enter your text or URL, choose a color, and tap \'Generate\'. You can then save or share the image.</string>
